---

<PageLayout
	meta={{
		title: "Home",
		description: "Applied mathematician & HPC engineer. FOSS contributor and independent researcher.",
	}}
>
	<section>
		<h1 class="text-muted mb-4 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest">About</h1>
		<p class="text-accent mb-2 font-semibold">Applied mathematician & HPC engineer.</p>
		<p class="mb-8 max-w-prose">
			I work on high-performance computing systems, numerical methods, and parallel algorithms.
			Outside of work, I contribute to free and open-source software and pursue independent
			research — mostly at the intersection of mathematics, computing, and physics.
		</p>
		<SocialList />
	</section>
</PageLayout>
